<Document>
  <name>Live Oak County — Unmapped Historical Markers</name>
  <description>THC markers in Live Oak County without an HMDB id (isMissing excluded). 1 with THC coords; 0 geocoded from address; 5 omitted (no usable address).</description>
  <Placemark>
    <name>VFW and American Legion War Memorial</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Live Oak County Courthouse lawn, Houston Street at Guadalupe, George West<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> 301 Houston Street, George West<br/><br/><b>Marker Text:</b> In memory of those who served, and gave their lives for freedom and defense of their country.]]></description>
    <Point><coordinates>-98.114211,28.334174,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
